summary: The Make America Healthy Again movement cites soda as one reason for bad diets. The big beverage companies aren’t going down without a fight.

headline: 3 Consumer Stocks with Mounting Challenges
summary: Consumer staples are considered safe havens in turbulent markets due to their inelastic demand profiles. But recently, the industry has failed to do its job as it shed 13.9% over the past six months. This performance was much worse than the S&P 500’s 1.9% loss.
